data.title: Martha, Viscountess of Marsan
data.meta_description: Martha of Marsan was a ruling Viscountess of Marsan. She was suo jure Viscountess of Marsan, which she inherited from her father.
data.text: Martha of Marsan (1228 - 1283) (also known as Mathe or Amata) was a ruling Viscountess of Marsan. She was suo jure Viscountess of Marsan, which she inherited from her father.
